name: of the Wolf
note:
<Prefix Suffix Effect>
var atkBonus = Math.floor(this.averagePartyLevel() / 4);
if (atkBonus > 0) {
    newItem.params[2] += atkBonus;
    newItem.name += " (+" + atkBonus + ")";
    newItem.price += atkBonus*10;
}
</Prefix Suffix Effect>
